### 1. Java List<MemberDTO> -> JSON 배열
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/members

### 2. java MemberDTO -> JSON 객체
GET http://localhost:8080/api/vi/members/1

### 3. JSON 요청 본문 -> MemberDTO
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/members
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "no": 5,
  "name": "호랑이",
  "age": 3,
  "enrollDate": "2026-05-29 10:35:00"
}

### 4. message + data 응답 구조
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/members/response-wrapper

### 5. ObjectMapper 직접 변환 확인
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/members/object-mapper


